---
title: Italian Cheesy Chicken Burger & Caramelised Onion with Dill-Parsley Mayo & Fries
description: Bring a little Italian flair to burger night by using classic flavours such as tomato, Italian herbs, Parmesan and dill-parsley mayo to turn a tender chicken fillet into a filling supreme burger.
